Package com.cloudpos.msr

Provide access to the MSR device.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MSRDevice
    The MSRDevice interface defines the MSR APIs to be used by the applications.
    MSRDeviceSpec
    The MSRDeviceSpec interface defines the specification of the MSR device.
    MSROperationResult
    MSROperationResults are generated by the Magnetic Stripe Reader device implementation to notify the application of the completion of a requested operation.
    MSRTrackData
    The data object of the track.
